823
01:05:44,333 --> 01:05:47,333
Well I hope she knows
what she's getting into.

824
01:05:47,416 --> 01:05:48,250
Yeah.

825
01:05:50,208 --> 01:05:52,416
So I'm just gonna go right ahead and uh,

826
01:05:53,458 --> 01:05:55,167
