855
01:07:39,041 --> 01:07:40,042
Me too.

856
01:07:40,125 --> 01:07:41,750
Um, call me?

857
01:07:41,833 --> 01:07:43,458
Yeah, of course.

858
01:07:43,541 --> 01:07:44,375
Cool.

859
01:07:45,958 --> 01:07:47,417
I'll see you soon.

860
01:07:47,500 --> 01:07:48,500
- Bye.
- Bye.

