863
01:08:08,541 --> 01:08:13,541
(Eerie, humming music) (Rustling grass)

864
01:08:28,416 --> 01:08:33,416
(Woman screams) (Dark, ominous music)

865
01:08:36,875 --> 01:08:38,292
Maybe he's right,

866
01:08:38,375 --> 01:08:40,875
I don't wanna experience
anything paranormal.

