874
01:09:00,416 --> 01:09:01,375
When was this?

875
01:09:01,458 --> 01:09:02,750
I don't know, exactly.

876
01:09:02,833 --> 01:09:04,792
It sounds like quite a few years ago.

877
01:09:04,875 --> 01:09:06,708
Mayra says people claim to have seen her

878
