879
01:09:09,500 --> 01:09:10,333
That's it.

880
01:09:11,416 --> 01:09:12,208
What?

881
01:09:12,291 --> 01:09:14,333
Grandma was telling me that

882
01:09:14,416 --> 01:09:16,667
demonic spirits attach themselves

883
01:09:16,750 --> 01:09:18,708
