923
01:12:14,750 --> 01:12:16,375
- It's good.
- Isn't it?

924
01:12:16,458 --> 01:12:18,375
I might have to get
another one before we leave.

925
01:12:18,458 --> 01:12:20,042
(Mayra laughs)

926
01:12:20,125 --> 01:12:22,167
(People chattering)

927
01:12:22,250 --> 01:12:24,625
So, I'm sorry to hear

928
01:12:24,708 --> 01:12:26,833
