fasting for you and your family.

1037
01:20:28,333 --> 01:20:31,333
Now is the time for us to fight.

1038
01:20:32,750 --> 01:20:37,750
(Engine humming) (Quiet, eerie music)

1039
01:21:05,125 --> 01:21:07,541
